00:24:56,616 --> 00:24:58,249
Stop it this minute.

473
00:24:58,284 --> 00:25:00,952
I have to go change for lunch.

474
00:25:02,422 --> 00:25:05,790
It's $200 including the tip.

475
00:25:07,374 --> 00:25:11,933
_

476
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:14,599
- He gave me a check for $500.
- Like a whore?

477
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:19,743
_

478
00:25:20,034 --> 00:25:22,420
_

479
00:25:22,421 --> 00:25:24,181
_

