00:25:24,182 --> 00:25:26,608
_

481
00:25:27,530 --> 00:25:29,897
In the States,
it's the 20th century.

482
00:25:29,949 --> 00:25:31,282
People get divorced
all the time.

483
00:25:31,317 --> 00:25:34,619
Exactly.
You can still get an annulment.

484
00:25:34,654 --> 00:25:36,454
I'm not like you.

485
00:25:36,489 --> 00:25:38,656
I don't spend my whole life
feeling ashamed.

486
00:25:38,657 --> 00:25:40,150
_

487
00:25:40,159 --> 00:25:42,210
Marie-France,
don't be a bitch.

488
00:25:42,245 --> 00:25:44,745
I am not a servant here
to wait on her

489
00:25:44,797 --> 00:25:46,581
while she goes for lunch.

490
00:25:46,633 --> 00:25:48,716
I know you don't
understand this,

491
00:25:48,751 --> 00:25:50,167
but it's for my career.

492
00:25:51,504 --> 00:25:53,304
Good luck with
your bright future.

493
00:25:55,141 --> 00:25:56,674
Wait.

494
00:25:56,675 --> 00:25:59,721
_

495
00:25:59,722 --> 00:26:01,422
_

