00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:13,234
( sighs )

500
00:26:13,693 --> 00:26:16,494
It's not much.
It's just the boxes,

501
00:26:16,529 --> 00:26:19,363
Granny's cabinet,
that chair, and the mirror.

502
00:26:19,365 --> 00:26:21,866
Go. Have fun.

503
00:26:21,918 --> 00:26:24,035
I'll take care of this.

504
00:26:24,036 --> 00:26:26,414
_

505
00:26:33,129 --> 00:26:35,546
Hey, where's everybody going?

506
00:26:35,548 --> 00:26:38,382
Oh, my mother's here.
Thank you so much.

507
00:26:47,434 --> 00:26:49,300
Do you have to smoke in here?

508
00:26:49,352 --> 00:26:51,185
It's taking my mind
off your driving.

509
00:26:51,221 --> 00:26:53,221
[ <i>"The Train" playing</i> ]

510
00:26:53,273 --> 00:26:55,189
I don't know why we couldn't
